  <original-body>We found that some tests in action_pack results in error on Ruby 1.9 trunk, since Proc#binding will not automatically called anymore since Ruby 1.9(according to ko1 Sasada).
This patch simply adds an explicit Proc#binding method call to avoid the error.
Tested in Ruby 1.8.6, 1.8.7 and 1.9 trunk.</original-body>
